technology.%20I%20live%20in%20a%20city%20that%20arranges%20watch-parties%20for%20OpenAI%20announcements.%20I%20appreciate%20conversational%20AI%20and%20ChatGPT%20for%20helping%20me%20with%20the%20work%20I%20do%20as%20a%20writer%2C%20journalist%2C%20and%20marketer%20for%20start-ups%20and%20other%20companies.%20I've%20even%20trained%20it%20to%20be%20a%20customised%20therapist%20of%20sorts%2C%20someone%20I%20can%20text%20anytime%20I%20have%20some%20emotional%20turmoil.%20OpenAI%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsam-altman-s-net-worth-touches-the-2-billion-mark-and-not-because-of-openai-5166857%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20a%20one-word%20comment%20about%20people%20like%20me%3A%20%26quot%3Bher%26quot%3B%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Joaquin%20Phoenix%20film%20in%20which%20he%2C%20a%20lonely%20writer%2C%20falls%20in%20love%20with%20Scarlett-Johannsen-as-a-computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%20-%20or%20not%20-%20I'm%20not%20so%20lonely%20in%20my%20feelings%20of%20simultaneous%20awe%20and%20worry.%20Even%20tech%20enthusiasts%20and%20optimists%20are%20becoming%20doomers%2C%20expecting%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAella_Girl%2Fstatus%2F1790618794181976397%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bwe're%20all%20dead%20from%20AI%20in%2010-15%20years%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Amidst%20this%20palpably%20tense%20imagination%20of%20Big%20Tech%2C%20it's%20curious%20that%20somebody%20at%20Apple%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20advertise%20the%20latest%20iPad%20Pro%20by%20showing%20a%20hydraulic%20press%20crushing%20a%20trumpet%2C%20a%20bust%2C%20a%20piano%2C%20some%20camera%20lenses%2C%20stationery%2C%20and%20art%20supplies%2C%20set%20to%20jaunty%20music%20in%20an%20industrial%20garage.%20Quintessential%20tools%20of%20human%20creativity%20become%20pulp%2C%20but%2C%20fortunately%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20this%20crushing%20(!)%20is%20the%20thinnest%20iPad%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrushed%20By%20%3Cem%3ECrush!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20podcaster%20and%20self-professed%20'on-and-off%20trumpet%20player%20for%20decades'%20felt%20harrowed%20by%20the%20hydraulic%20press%20starting%20with%20a%20trumpet%2C%20he%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20exactly%20what%20this%20ad%20made%20me%20feel.%20Crushed%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20another%20LinkedIn%20member.%20Even%20Paul%20Graham%2C%20founder%20of%20Y-Combinator%20and%20veritable%20technology%20brother%2C%20opined%20that%20%26quot%3BSteve%20%5BJobs%5D%20wouldn't%20have%20shipped%20that%20ad.%20It%20would%20have%20pained%20him%20too%20much%20to%20watch.%26quot%3B%20Apple%20apologised%20for%20the%20ad%20two%20days%20later.%20They%20withdrew%20it%20from%20televisions%20in%20America%2C%20but%20it%20remains%20on%20their%20social%20media%20and%20YouTube%2C%20with%20over%202%20million%20views%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ire%20is%20understandable%20considering%20%3Cem%3ECrush!%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20made%20by%20the%20same%20company%20that%20released%20%3Cem%3E1984%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20the%20year%201984.%20Directed%20by%20Ridley%20Scott%2C%20that%20classic%20ad-film%20showed%20a%20spunky%20young%20woman%20throwing%20a%20hammer%20at%20Big%20Brother%20as%20he%20addressed%20citizens%20all%20dressed%20in%20the%20same%20drab%20grey%2C%20implying%20that%20Apple's%20release%20of%20the%20Macintosh%20would%20help%20conformists%20break%20free.%20The%20year%201984%20wouldn't%20be%20like%20George%20Orwell's%20dystopian%20imagination%20of%20it.%20Apple%20became%20the%20company%20with%20an%20original%2C%20utopian%20vision%20of%20technology.%20Allaying%20fears%20that%20machines%20would%20be%20tools%20of%20surveillance%2C%20it%20positioned%20them%20instead%20as%20a%20means%20to%20unfettered%20individual%20creativity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Finappropriate-when-olas-ai-chatbot-disagreed-with-ceo-bhavishs-pronoun-remark-5654359%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Blog%3A%20'Inappropriate'%20-%20When%20Ola%20Chatbot%20Disagreed%20With%20CEO%20Bhavish's%20Comments%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20%3Cem%3ECrush!%3C%2Fem%3E%20even%20sadder%2C%20apart%20from%20this%20lost%20vision%20and%20Tarantino-esque%20attempt%20at%20destruction%20alongside%20melody%2C%20is%20that%20it%20was%20probably%20never%20original.%20A%202015%20LG%20ad%20first%20showed%20several%20creative%20instruments%20being%20hydraulic-pressed%20into%20a%20new%2015-megapixel%20camera%20-%208GB%20microSD%20card%20included.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20OpenAI%20and%20Google%20can%20market%20themselves%20through%20the%20sheer%20technological%20leaps%20they%20are%20announcing%20(people%20noticed%20the%20simplicity%20of%20their%20presentation%20and%20events)%2C%20more%20traditional%20Big%20Tech%20products%20are%20struggling%20to%20present%20their%20innovations%20in%20a%20positive%20light.%20One%20of%20Meta's%20Superbowl%20ads%20tried%20to%20build%20excitement%20about%20the%20virtual%20world%20by%20showing%20some%20dogs%20finding%20escape%20from%20the%20real%20world%20in%20it.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fai-necessary-to-help-create-healthier-dating-experiences-bumble-founder-whitney-wolfe-herd-5646373%5C%22%3EDating%20app%20Bumble's%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20announced%20that%20the%20future%20of%20dating%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fai-is-reshaping-romance-virtual-avatars-to-go-on-dates-on-your-behalf-5673578%5C%22%3EAI%20concierges%20dating%20other%20AI%20concierges%20for%20you.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Did%20Tech%20Start%20Scaring%20People%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20present%20such%20formidable%20leaps%20in%20technology%20to%20an%20audience%20that%20feels%20threatened%20by%20it%20-%20perhaps%20for%20good%20reason%2C%20considering%20the%20quantum%20of%20change%20and%20displacement%20these%20products%20will%20instigate%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAutomation%2C%20it%20was%20long%20believed%2C%20would%20affect%20only%20repetitive%20manual%20labour.%20But%2C%20much%20faster%20than%20even%20AI%20experts%20predicted%2C%20generative%20AI%20now%20emulates%20human%20creative%20work%2C%20manipulates%20language%20and%20knowledge%2C%20and%20keeps%20getting%20smarter%2C%20just%20as%20humans%20do.%20AI-generated%20images%20and%20videos%20are%20already%20interfering%20in%20the%202024%20US%20Presidential%20elections%2C%20as%20well%20as%20India's%20general%20elections.%20AI%20was%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Hollywood%20writers'%20strike%2C%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20labour%20extends%20to%20most%20white-collar%20professions%2C%20even%20coding%2C%20marketing%2C%20advertising%2C%20medicine%2C%20military%20operations%2C%20et%20cetera.%20Former%20Google%20whistleblower%20and%20Signal%20CEO%20Meredith%20Whittaker%20explained%20that%20anxiety%20best%20in%20a%20chat%20with%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20talking%20about%20is%20laying%20claim%20to%20the%20creative%20output%20of%20millions%2C%20billions%20of%20people%20and%20then%20using%20that%20to%20create%20systems%20that%20are%20directly%20undermining%20their%20livelihoods.%26quot%3B%20In%20Singapore%2C%20writers%20and%20publishers%20are%20on%20strike%20rejecting%20their%20governments'%20plans%20to%20train%20AI%20on%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESam%20Altman%2C%20Man%20Of%20The%20Moment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20the%20seat%20of%20tech-utopian%20thinking%20has%20shifted%20from%20Apple%20to%20the%20only%20man%20capable%20of%20it%20in%20the%20AI%20era%2C%20a%20man%20whose%20job%20depends%20on%20it%2C%20and%20the%20man%20responsible%20for%20it.%20Sam%20Altman%20has%20been%20called%20the%20'Oppenheimer'%20of%20our%20age.%20In%20a%202021%20essay%20called%20%3Cem%3EMoore's%20Law%20for%20Everything%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Altman%20posited%20that%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20make%20everything%20better%20and%20cheaper%20(Moore's%20Law%20predicted%20that%20the%20number%20of%20transistors%20to%20fit%20on%20an%20integrated%20circuit%20would%20double%20each%20year%2C%20implying%20that%20computers%20and%20computing%20power%20would%20become%20exponentially%20faster%2C%20cheaper%20and%20smaller%20over%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Altman%2C%20AI%20will%20achieve%20this%20effect%20of%20improving%20performance%20and%20reducing%20costs%20in%20multiple%20aspects%20of%20daily%20life.%20%26quot%3BImagine%20a%20world%20where%2C%20for%20decades%2C%20everything-housing%2C%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%2C%20etc.-became%20half%20as%20expensive%20every%20two%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes.%20The%20OpenAI%20CEO%20-%20who%20says%20GPT-4o%20is%20already%20twice%20as%20fast%20and%20half%20as%20expensive%20as%20its%20predecessor%20-%20envisions%20a%20utopia%20involving%20phenomenal%20wealth%2C%20instigating%20such%20radical%20shifts%20in%20society%20that%20policy%20will%20have%20to%20be%20equally%20radical%20to%20keep%20up.%20The%20challenge%20is%20ensuring%20equitable%20access%20to%20resources%20that%20allow%20everyone%20to%20live%20this%20free%2C%20creative%2C%20comfortable%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fai-chatbot-goes-rogue-swears-at-customer-and-slams-company-in-uk-4900202%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0AI%20Chatbot%20Goes%20Rogue%2C%20Swears%20At%20Customer%20And%20Slams%20Company%20In%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20he%20has%20various%20recommendations%3A%20A%20board%20of%20experts%20and%20professionals%20-%20not%20politicians%20-%20governing%20how%20AI%20should%20be%20regulated%20and%20used%2C%20as%20has%20been%20done%20with%20nuclear%20power%3B%20universal%20basic%20income%3B%20taxation%20on%20land%20and%20capital%2C%20instead%20of%20property%20and%20labour%2C%20implying%2C%20basically%2C%20that%20this%20increased%20growth%20and%20wealth%20would%20be%20appropriately%20re-distributed%20amongst%20citizens.%20He's%20honest%20enough%20to%20admit%20that%20AI%20will%20eliminate%20some%20jobs%20(customer%20service%20and%20call%20centre%20employees%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20chatbots%2C%20he's%20sure)%20but%20he's%20also%20confident%20that%20as%20with%20every%20technological%20revolution%20in%20the%20past%2C%20there%20will%20be%20new%20jobs%20and%20abundance%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20improve%20capitalism%20is%20to%20enable%20everyone%20to%20benefit%20from%20it%20directly%20as%20an%20equity%20owner.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20new%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20it%20will%20be%20newly%20feasible%20as%20AI%20grows%20more%20powerful%2C%20because%20there%20will%20be%20dramatically%20more%20wealth%20to%20go%20around.%20The%20two%20dominant%20sources%20of%20wealth%20will%20be%201)%20companies%2C%20particularly%20ones%20that%20make%20use%20of%20AI%2C%20and%202)%20land%2C%20which%20has%20a%20fixed%20supply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECredit%20Where%20Due%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20humans%20in%20such%20a%20society%20will%20be%20up%20to%20them%2C%20Altman%20believes.%20There%20will%20be%20people%20who%20do%20not%20want%20to%20work%2C%20and%20instead%20dedicate%20themselves%20to%20life%20in%20nature%2C%20care%2C%20or%20service%20to%20other%20beings.%20But%20there%20will%20also%20be%20people%20who%20want%20to%20work%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20economy%2C%20using%20AI%20to%20augment%20what%20they%20already%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20this%20barely%20novel%20idea%20-%20a%20utopian%20society%20where%20technology%20allows%20humanity%20to%20flourish%2C%20with%20basic%20needs%20all%20taken%20care%20of%2C%20plenty%20of%20time%20for%20leisure%2C%20work%20as%20discretionary%2C%20and%20equitably%20distributed%20capital%20-%20has%20its%20origins%20in%20another%20radical%20thin