%20rioters%2C%20including%20between%203%2C000%20and%204%2C000%20in%20the%20capital%20Noumea%2C%20France's%20High%20Commissioner%20Louis%20Le%20Franc%20said%20in%20a%20televised%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20hundred%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20and%2064%20gendarmes%20and%20police%20injured%2C%20while%20road%20barricades%20put%20up%20by%20the%20protesters%20were%20causing%20a%20%26quot%3Bdire%20situation%26quot%3B%20for%20medicine%20and%20food%20for%20the%20population%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20in%20New%20Caledonia%20that%20came%20in%20force%20at%205%20a.m.%20local%20time%20(1800%20GMT%20Wednesday)%2C%20giving%20authorities%20additional%20powers%20to%20ban%20gatherings%20and%20forbid%20people%20from%20moving%20around%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20reinforcements%20adding%20500%20officers%20to%20the%201%2C800%20usually%20present%20on%20the%20island%2C%20have%20been%20sent%20after%20rioters%20torched%20vehicles%20and%20businesses%20and%20looted%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoumea%20resident%20Yoan%20Fleurot%20told%20Reuters%20in%20a%20Zoom%20interview%20that%20he%20has%20seen%20looting%20and%20destruction%20of%20properties.%20Some%20storeowners%20willingly%20let%20their%20shelves%20be%20raided%2C%20pleading%20that%20their%20shops%20not%20be%20destroyed%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFleurot%20said%20he%20is%20armed%20with%20a%2016-caliber%20gun%20and%20has%20video%20surveillance%20installed%20around%20his%20house%2C%20adding%20he%20has%20only%20ventured%20out%20in%20daylight%20to%20check%20on%20his%20parents%20or%20his%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20roadblocks%20were%20difficult%20to%20pass%20through%2C%20and%20he%20been%20subjected%20to%20insults%20and%20threats%20of%20violence%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20New%20Caledonian%2C%20but%20I%20no%20longer%20know%20my%20country%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26