there%20will%20be%20100%20per%20cent%20cloud%20cover%20at%20night%20with%20around%2062%20per%20cent%20chance%20of%20rain.%20There%20might%20be%20a%20few%20thunderstorms%20as%20well.%20The%20temperature%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20will%20drop%20to%20around%2021-22%20degree%20celsius%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20not%20a%20washout%2C%20the%20continuous%20rainfall%20might%20reduce%20the%20probablity%20of%20a%20full%20game.%20As%20per%20the%20IPL%20playing%20conditions%2C%20the%20shortest%20game%20that%20can%20take%20place%20is%20five%20overs%20which%20can%20begin%20latest%20by%2010%3A56%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fq35611ho_rcb-vs-csk-weather-forecast_625x300_16_May_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs'%20concerned%2C%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20and%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20have%20already%20sealed%20the%20berth%20for%20themselves%2C%20while%20a%20total%20of%20five%20teams%20are%20still%20in%20race%20for%20the%20remaining%20two%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%2C%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%2C%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20RCB%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20are%20the%20teams%20fighting%20for%20the%20top-4%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDC%20have%20exhausted%20their%20quota%20of%20league%20matches%2C%20beating%20LSG%20in%20their%20final%20game%20to%20achieve%2014%20points%20from%20as%20many%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20other%20contenders%2C%20barring%20SRH%2C%20all%20the%20other%20teams%20have%20only%20one%20match%20remaining.%20It%20means%20that%20net%20run-rates%20will%20most%20probably%20come%20in%20to%20play%20to%20decide%20the%20final%20spot%20for%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RCB%20vs%20CSK%20clash%2C%20however%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20most%20crucial%20with%20fans%20and