%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harris%2C%20the%20first-ever%20Indian%20American%2C%20African%20American%2C%20and%20a%20woman%20to%20be%20elected%20as%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20US%20told%20a%20packed%20room%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20there%20are%20five%20elected%20Indian%20American%20members%20of%20the%20Congress%20--%20Dr%20Ami%20Bera%2C%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthi%2C%20Ro%20Khanna%2C%20Pramila%20Jayapal%2C%20and%20Shri%20Thanedar.%20Impact%20believed%20that%20in%202024%2C%20the%20Indian%20American%20strength%20in%20the%20Congress%20will%20increase%20to%2010%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tightly%20contested%20presidential%20race%2C%20Impact%20said%20Indian%20American%20voters%20--%20the%20second%20largest%20immigrant%20community%20and%20fastest%20growing%20in%20many%20states%20--%20could%20be%20the%20decisive%20margin%20of%20victory%20in%20key%20races%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20being%20done%20by%20Impact%2C%20Harris%20said%20in%20her%20opening%20remarks%2C%20is%20extraordinary%20as%20she%20applauded%20the%20role%20of%20the%20think%20tank%20and%20its%20members%20in%20electing%20not%20only%20members%20of%20the%20community%20but%20also%20in%20electing%20Senators%20in%20states%20like%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20really%20is%20extraordinary.%20I%20wanted%20to%20stop%20by%20to%20thank%20of%20course%20the%20organisation%20for%20everything%20and%20for%20all%20that%20it%20represents%2C%20but%20also%20to%20say%20especially%20to%20those%20who%20have%20run%20for%20office%20or%20aspire%20to%20run%20for%20office%2C%20that%20you%20must%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20must%20know%20that%20you%20are%20not%20alone.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20that%20we%20still%20have%20to%20do%20as%20a%20country%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20work%20that%20we%20each%20do%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20are%20here%20together%2C%20is%20born%20out%20of%20a%20belief%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20America.%20And%20dare%20I%20say%20that%2C%20I%20am%20empirical%20evidence%20of%20the%20promise%20of%20America%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20election%20coming%20up%20in%20six%20months%2C%20I%20think%20is%20presenting%20a%20question%20to%20each%20of%20us.%20Which%20is%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20world%20do%20we%20want%20to%20live%20in%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20country%20do%20we%20want%20to%20live%20in%3F%20And%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20that%20we%20answer%20that%20question%20is%20to%20seek%20office%20and%20to%20participate%20in%20elections%20knowing%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20those%20elections%20matter%20in%20fundamental%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harris%20said%20as%20she%20asked%20the%20members%20of%20the%20audience%20to%20raise%20their%20hands%20if%20they%20were%20running%20for%20office%20or%20planning%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20will%20happen%2C%20invariably%20it's%20happened%20to%20all%20of%20us%2C%20is%20you%20are%20going%20to%20find%20yourself%20invariably%20in%20rooms%20where%20you%20are%20the%20only%20one%20who%20looks%20like%20you%2C%20the%20only%20one%20who%20has%20had%20your%20life%20experience.%20What%20I%20then%20say%20to%20you%20each%2C%20look%20around%20this%20room%20and%20hold%20onto%20this%20image.%20And%20remember%20then%20when%20you%20walk%20into%20those%20rooms%2C%20when%20you%20walk%20into%20those%20situations%2C%20you%20remember%2C%20you%20are%20not%20alone.%20We%20are%20all%20there%20with%20you.%20You%20must%20remember%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20Impact%20co-founder%20and%20treasurer%20Deepak%20Raj%20said%20Harris%20was%20instrumental%20in%20its%20formation%20eight%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20has%20been%20an%20incredible%20guiding%20force%20for%20this%20organisation%20over%20the%20duration.%20She%20came%20to%20the%20first%20summit%20in%202018%20and%20here%20she%20is%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%20said%20Harris%20is%20not%20only%20the%20first%20woman%20but%20the%20first%20South%20Asian%20Indian%20American%20woman%2C%20to%20be%20elected%20as%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20has%20been%20an%20incredible%20role%20model%2C%20I%20think%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20What%20she%20has%20done%20is%20she%20has%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20women%2C%20for%20immigrants%20and%20minorities%20and%20is%20a%20true%20hero%20and%20an%20inspiration%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20her%20success%2C%20what%20she%20has%20achieved%2C%20gives%20us%20the%20hope%20and%20the%20confidence%20that%20we%20have%20a%20bright%20future%2C%20all%20of%20us%20together%20fighting%20for%20public%20office%20and%20as%20a%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20vice%20president%20took%20the%20stage%2C%20some%20briefly%20chanted%20%E2%80%9CFour%20more%20years.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20one%20person%20yelled%20%E2%80%9CShame%20on%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20appeared%20to%20be%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20clear.%20The%20protester%20was%20soon%20removed%20from%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20also%20spoke%20about%20her%20mom%20coming%20to%20the%20US%20from%20India%20when%20she%20was%2019%20years%20old%20and%20marching%20for%20Civil%20Rights%20in%20Berkeley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20growing%20up%2C%20she%20would%20visit%20India%20every%20two%20years%20and%20her%20grandfather%20would%20take%20her%20on%20morning%20walks.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20remember%20as%20a%20young%20girl%E2%80%A6%20hearing%20them%20discuss%20the%20importance%20of%20standing%20for%20what%20is%20right%20and%20fairness%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%