eling%20her%20%26quot%3Breal%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20sees%20it%20as%20just%20as%20authentic%20and%20valid%20as%20the%20stationary%20alternative.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20tucked%20into%20a%20bowl%20of%20wisp-thin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foldest-soup-in-world-wattana-panich-bangkok-food-thailand-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThai%20rice%20noodles%3C%2Fa%3E%20studded%20with%20bok%20choy%20and%20sprinkled%20with%20fried%20garlic%2C%20all%20I%20could%20do%20was%20wax%20poetic%20about%20Buffalo%20wings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlastic%20spoon%20in%20one%20hand%2C%20chopsticks%20in%20the%20other%2C%20I%20described%20my%20hometown's%20finest%20fare%2C%20which%20included%20hot%2C%20buttery%20chicken%20wings.%20My%20favorite%20basket%20always%20came%20from%20a%20local%20dive%20bar%20in%20Western%20New%20York%2C%2015%20miles%20from%20Niagara%20Falls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20three%20years%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-couple-house-rural-thailand-debt-free-slow-life-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elived%20in%20Thailand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20few%20Chang%20beers%20or%20a%20familiar%20Garth%20Brooks%20song%20about%20friends%20in%20low%20places%20would%20often%20prompt%20me%20to%20crave%20a%20seat%20at%20that%20bar%2C%208%2C533%20miles%20across%20the%20ocean%2C%20with%20wings%20on%20one%20side%20and%20Reuben%20fries%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20years%20of%20teaching%20English%2C%20working%20at%20summer%20camps%20in%20the%20far%20north%20of%20Thailand%2C%20and%20spending%20long%20weekends%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsleeper-train-overnight-thailand-bangkok-chiang-mai-review-tickets-guide-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploring%20the%20country%20by%20train%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20Buffalo.%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20bathe%20my%20eager%20tastebuds%20in%20all%20the%20Frank's%20hot%20sauce%20and%20meaty%20wings%20and%20wash%20it%20down%20with%20an%20ice-cold%20Loganberry%20soda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20everything%20was%20different.%20The%20old%20classic%20dishes%20didn't%20offer%20the%20culinary%20homecoming%20I'd%20been%20hoping%20for.%20Instead%2C%20I%20got%20horrid%20stomach%20cramps%20and%20acute%20nausea.%20The%20Buffalo%20wing%20mythology%20no%20longer%20held%20up.%20More%20importantly%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f11ff5ba-994d-403e-a6e0-5b3d637957f9%5C%22%3EMy%20%26quot%3B6-month%26quot%3B%20journey%20to%20Thailand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20breaking%20up%20with%20my%20long-term%20boyfriend%2C%20crashing%20my%20car%2C%20and%20quitting%20my%20job%20%E2%80%94%20in%20that%20order%20%E2%80%94%20I%20moved%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-lotus-season-3-hotel-location-thailand-resort-four-seasons-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKoh%20Samui%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20told%20everyone%20I'd%20be%20back%20in%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20six%20months%20passed%20on%20the%20tropical%20island%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Thailand%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20heading%20home%2C%20I%20made%20a%20visa%20run%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flao-china-railway-train-ride-countryside-burned-photos-laos-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThai-Laos%20border%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20stay%20for%20longer.%20It%20would%20be%20my%20first%20of%20many%2C%20extending%20my%20initial%20six%20months%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20hooked%20on%20the%20steamy%20weather%2C%20the%20beaches%20with%20water%20the%20color%20of%20blue%20topaz%2C%20and%20the%20food.%20The%20ice-cold%20pineapples%20tasted%20as%20sweet%20as%20sponge%20candy%20(a%20treat%20from%20Buffalo%20similar%20to%20toffee).%20Lunch%20usually%20included%20spicy%20som%20tom%20with%20sour%20tamarind%2C%20peanuts%2C%20and%20shrimp%2C%2