l%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portal%20between%20New%20York%20City%20and%20Dublin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20giant%20video%20installation%20livestreaming%20between%20the%20two%20locations%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20shut%20down%20due%20to%20bad%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20terrible.%20The%20portal%20should%20reopen!%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20should%20have%20portals%20all%20over%20the%20country%2C%20all%20over%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20connecting%20two%20random%20places.%20We%20should%20have%20a%20portal%20between%20Miami%20and%20Tokyo%2C%20Florence%20and%20Dubai%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Stockholm.%20Currently%2C%20there's%20a%20portal%20between%20cities%20in%20Lithuania%20and%20Poland%2C%20but%20let's%20dream%20even%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20a%20world%20where%20technology%20can%20feel%20menacing.%20We%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-biggest-fears-risk-threat-chatgpt-openai-google-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworry%20about%20what%20AI%20is%20doing%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20information%20we%20consume%2C%20the%20art%20we%20see%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20it%20might%20degrade%20both.%20This%20week%2C%20OpenAI%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-io-2024-live-updates-ai-search-android-announcements-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20debuted%20new%20ways%20to%20interact%20with%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20OpenAI's%20voice%20assistant%20drew%20comparisons%20to%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BHer%26quot%3B%20in%20ways%20that%20were%20both%20flattering%20and%20dystopian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20portal%20is%20a%20case%20of%20technology%20that's%20just%20pure%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20simple%2C%20there's%20nothing%20too%20deep%20to%20think%20about.%20It's%20not%20even%20%26quot%3Bnew%26quot%3B%20tech%20%E2%80%94%20video%20streaming%20between%20two%20locations%20is%20not%20exactly%20novel%2C%20although%20I%20suppose%20%26quot%3Bit's%20really%20big%26quot%3B%20differentiates%20it%20from%2C%20say%2C%20FaceTime.%20The%20situation%20is%20what%20makes%20it%20different%20%E2%80%94%20video%20chatting%20technology%20is%20usually%20personal%2C%20used%20at%20home%20or%20in%20your%20office%20conference%20room.%20Putting%20it%20in%20a%20public%20space%2C%20with%20other%20strangers%20%E2%80%94%20that%20makes%20it%20fun%20and%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pure%20and%20human%20to%20be%20curious%20about%20strangers%20in%20another%20country%2C%20to%20be%20excited%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20seeing%20someone%20else%20across%20the%20screen%2C%20knowing%20they%20can%20see%20you%2C%20too.%20It's%20fun.%20It's%20delightful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20there%20was%20some%20bad%20behavior%20during%20the%20NYC-Dublin%20link-up.%20New%20Yorkers%20taunted%20the%20Dubliners%20with%20potatoes%3B%20a%20Dubliner%20held%20up%20a%20photo%20of%209%2F11.%20Someone%20in%20Dublin%20mooned%20the%20New%20Yorkers%2C%20and%20then%20there%20was%20the%20woman%20who%20flashed%20her%20breasts%20to%20the%20Dubliners.%20Not%20ideal%20(although%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2013%2F05%2F16%2Fnyregion%2Fa-police-roll-call-reminder-women-may-go-topless.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeven%20necessarily%20illegal%20in%20NYC%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20flasher%20was%20a%20really%20specific%20case%20%E2%80%94%20she%20is%20a%20TikTok%20and%20OnlyFans%20influencer%20named%20Ava%20Louise%20who%20has%20also%20been%20involved%20in%20some%20other%20headline-grabbing%20scenarios%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F05%2F15%2Fus-news%2Fonlyfans-model-who-flashed-nyc-dublin-portal-same-woman-who-told-dr-phil-shed-rather-die-hot-than-live-ugly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elicking%20a%20plane%20toilet%20seat%20during%20Covid%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkanye-west-jeffree-star-rumors-dating-ava-louise-hoax-tiktok-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C