20simply%20using%20voice%20commands%20and%20monitor%20your%20food%20from%20your%20smartphone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20many%20hours%20of%20research%2C%20interviewing%20experts%2C%20and%20testing%20five%20microwaves%20from%20reputable%20brands%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-microwave%5C%22%3Ebest%20microwaves%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20found%20that%20the%20GE%20Smart%20Microwave%20Oven%20is%20the%20best%20to%20have%20the%20essential%20features%20plus%20smart%20technology%20capabilities.%20Not%20only%20can%20you%20use%20it%20from%20your%20smartphone%20and%20by%20voice%20command%2C%20but%20it%20also%20features%20scan-to-cook%20technology%20where%20you%20can%20scan%20barcodes%20on%20pre-packaged%20foods%20to%20instantly%20display%20the%20correct%20cooking%20time%20and%20settings%2C%20so%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20say%20or%20press%20%26quot%3BStart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20it%20cooks%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20cooks%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20GE%20Smart%20Microwave%20Oven%20with%20its%20door%20open%20on%20a%20wood%20kitchen%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6042655d715c580018243088%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20registering%20just%20900%20watts%2C%20this%20GE%20microwave%20heats%20up%20quicker%20than%20expected%20on%20the%20defrost%2C%20potato%2C%20and%20dinner%20plate%20presets.%3Cp%3EFarima%20Ferguson%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ag.ndsu.edu%2Ffood%2Fhealth-and-nutrition%2Featsmart%2Feat-smart.-play-hard.-magazines-1%2F2014-2015-eat-smart.-play-hard.-magazine-1%2Fhave-you-done-the-marshmallow-test%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarshmallow%20test%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20noticed%20some%20hot%20spots%3A%20the%20outer%20edges%20and%20center%20cooked%20more%20quickly%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20marshmallows.%20Based%20on%20my%20experience%20testing%20other%20microwaves%2C%20these%20results%20indicate%20inconsistent%20cooking.%20I%20saw%20this%20again%20when%20I%20microwaved%20frozen%20mac%20and%20cheese%20according%20to%20the%20package%20instructions%20and%20noted%20that%20some%20parts%20were%20undercooked%20while%20others%20were%20overdone.%20In%20order%20to%20get%20consistent%20cooking%20out%20of%20this%20microwave%2C%20you'll%20definitely%20want%20to%20stop%20and%20stir%20your%20food%20during%20cooking%20to%20prevent%20hot%20spots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20900%20watts%2C%20this%20microwave%20isn't%20the%20most%20powerful%20(an%20average%20microwave%20is%20around%201%2C200%20watts)%2C%20but%20it%20heats%20up%20pretty%20quickly.%20Not%20only%20did%20the%20mac%20and%20cheese%20heat%20quicker%20than%20the%20package%20instructions%2C%20but%20the%20Defrost%2C%20Potato%2C%20and%20Dinner%20Plate%20presets%20all%20heated%20more%20quickly%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20capabilities%5C%22%3ESmart%20capabilities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close-up%20of%20a%20network%20label%20for%20the%20GE%20Smart%20Microwave%20Oven.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60426774715c580018243097%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20smart%20technology%20comes%20in%20handy%20if%20you're%20multitasking%20or%20in%20another%20room%20where%20you%20can't%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20your%20food%20in%20the%20microwave.%3Cp%3EFarima%20Ferguson%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20of%20having%20a%20smart%20microwave%20is%20that%20you%20can%20control%20the%20settings%20and%20check%20the%20status%20of%20your%20food%20from%20your%20smartphone%20or%20by%20using%20voice%20commands%20with%20a%20virtual%20assistant%20like%20Amazon%20Alexa%20or%20Google%20Assistant.%20I%20tested%20the%20microwave%20with%20my%20Google%20Home%20Mini.%20You%20can%20use%20the%20voice%20commands%20to%20prompt%20the%20microwave%20to%20perform%20different%20functions%20including%20start%2Fstop%2C%20set%20a%20specific%20cook%20time%2C%20and%20ask%20how%20much%20time%20is%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHands-free%20technology%20makes%20cooking%20more%20sanitary%2C%20reducing%20the%20amount%20of%20times%20you%20touch%20your%20microwave.%20This%20is%20especially%20helpful%20if%20you're%20prepping%20something%20like%20raw%20poultry.%20Overall%2C%20I%20find%20the%20app%20and%20voice%20commands%20are%20more%20of%20a%20convenience%20and%20sanitary%20benefit%20than%20a%20time%20saver%20since%20it%20doesn't%20take%20that%20much%20more%20effort%20to%20use%20the%20buttons%20manually.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Scan-to-cook%20function%5C%22%3EScan-to-cook%20function%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bcontrol%26quot%3B%20page%20in%20the%20GE%20Smart%20Microwave%20Oven%20smart%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60428a0144d8e300117b95af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScreenshot%20from%20the%20scan-to-cook%20setting%20in%20the%20product%20app%2C%20a%20feature%20that%20makes%20this%20microwave%20unique.%3Cp%3EFarima%20Ferguson%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it's%20cool%20that%20the%20cooking%20time%20and%20setting%20show%20up%20on%20the%20microwave%20just%20by%20scanning%20the%20barcode%20on%20the%20food%20package%2C%20it%20doesn't%20take%20that%20much%20longer%20to%20manually%20set%20the%20cooking%20time%20yourself.%20My%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20smart%20feature%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20check%20the%20status%20of%20your%20food%20from%20your%20phone%20or%20by%20asking%20your%20virtual%20assistant%20for%20a%20status%20update%20at%20any%20time%20during%20the%20heating%20process.%20Plus%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20has%20forgotten%20their%20food%20is%20in%20the%20microwave%20before%20I%20especially%20love%20getting%20an%20alert%20on%20my%20phone%20when%20my%20food%20is%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20bonus%20of%20the%20scan-to-cook%20technology%20is%20the%20ease%20of%20use.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20small%20kid%20who%20wants%20to%20warm%20up%20their%20favorite%20frozen%20meal%20after%20school%2C%20they%20can%20simply%20scan%20the%20barcode%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20read%20instructions%20on%20the%20package.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20always%20recommend%20supervising%20kids%20when%20they're%20using%20the%20microwave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20microwave%20heats%20quickly%2C%20it%20doesn't%20cook%20food%20as%20evenly%20as%20other%20microwaves%20I've%20tested.%20I%20found%20many%20hot%20spots%20when%20I%20experimented%20with%20the%20marshmallow%20test%2C%20and%20I%20even%20felt%20it%20warmed%20up%20my%20coffee%20unevenly.%20That%20said%2C%20it%20worked%20well%20for%20defrosting%20meat%2C%20making%20popcorn%2C%20and%20warming%20up%20leftovers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20GE%20first%20added%20Google%20Assistant%2C%20the%20voice%20commands%20were%20finicky%20with%20my%20Google%20Home%20Mini.%20It%20doesn't%20work%20unless%20you%20say%20the%20exact%20prompts.%20I%20actually%20had%20to%20call%20customer%20service%20because%20I%20couldn't%20get%20the%20voice%20commands%20to%20work%2C%20but%20their%20customer%20service%20was%20quick%20and%20helpful%2C%20and%20once%20I%20learned%20the%20exact%20voice%20commands%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221590%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pizza%20cooks%20inside%20the%20Tovala%20