0high%20mortgage%20rates%2C%20should%20you%20borrow%20against%20your%20home%20equity%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-now-time-for-heloc-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-we-evaluate-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20mortgages%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20row%20of%20three%20colorful%20houses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d330ed35cc0019e4a285%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20risen%2C%20HELOCs%20have%20become%20a%20more%20affordable%20alternative%20to%20a%20cash-out%20refinance.%3Cp%3EGlasshouse%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHELOCs%20are%20popular%20with%20homeowners%20who%20want%20to%20tap%20into%20home%20equity%20without%20replacing%20their%20current%20mortgage.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20HELOC%20is%20a%20type%20of%20second%20mortgage%20you%20use%20to%20borrow%20against%20a%20line%20of%20credit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20a%20HELOC%2C%20consider%20your%20overall