hat%20getting%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fis-cash-out-refinance-good-idea-right-now%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecash-out%20refinance%20doesn't%20make%20much%20sense%3C%2Fa%3E%20right%20now%2C%20because%20most%20homeowners%20have%20locked%20in%20rates%20that%20are%20well%20below%20what%20they%20would%20get%20by%20refinancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20access%20the%20equity%20they%20have%20in%20their%20homes%2C%20many%20homeowners%20have%20turned%20to%20second%20mortgages%2C%20including%20HELOCs%2C%20which%20don't%20require%20them%20to%20replace%20their%20mortgage%20and%20take%20on%20a%20higher%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20HELOC%2C%20you'll%20get%20a%20line%20of%20credit%20that%20borrows%20against%20your%20home%20equity.%20During%20the%20HELOC's%20draw%20period%2C%20you%20can%20draw%20any%20amount%20of%20money%20from%20the%20HELOC%2C%20up%20to%20the%20credit%20line.%20The%20draw%20period%20typically%20lasts%20up%20to%2010%20years%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20this%20period%20is%20up%2C%20the%20HELOC%20enters%20the%20repayment%20period%2C%20where%20you'll%20repay%20the%20loan%20and%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20borrow%20from%20your%20line%20of%20credit.%20This%20period%20can%20be%20as%20long%20as%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcitizens-bank-mortgage-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECitizens%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20HELOC%20lenders%20in%20the%20U.S.%2C%20has%20seen%20an%20uptick%20in%20HELOC%20interest%2C%20says%20Adam%20Boyd%2C%20head%20of%20home%20equity%20and%20unsecured%20lending%20at%20Citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20HELOC%20became%20a%20really%20attractive%20option%20for%20customers%20looking%20to%20tap%20into%20that%20equity%20and%20do%20it%20in%20a%20way%20without%20disrupting%20the%20rate%20on%20the%20first%20mortgage%2C%26quot%3B%20Boyd%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Today's%20HELOC%20rates%5C%22%3EToday's%20HELOC%20rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20consumer%20rates%20have%20been%20relatively%20high%20so%20far%20this%20year%20overall%2C%20HELOCs%20are%20often%20more%20affordable%20than%20other%20options%20like%20credit%20cards%20or%20personal%20loans.%20Plus%2C%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20drop%20later%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHELOC%20rates%20have%20generally%20remained%20between%208.16%25%20and%208.59%25%20this%20year%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20term%20length%20of%20the%20loan.%20Check%20out%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcurrent-heloc-rates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecurrent%20HELOC%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20page%20to%20see%20the%20latest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20much%20you%20could%20borrow%20with%20a%20HELOC%5C%22%3EHow%20much%20you%20could%20borrow%20with%20a%20HELOC%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Boyd%2C%20the%20average%20credit%20line%20size%20a%20HELOC%20borrower%20gets%20is%20around%20%24150%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20most%20borrowers%20aren't%20using%20the%20entire%20line%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20average%20utilization%20is%20on%20the%20order%20of%2035%25%20or%2040%25%20of%20the%20line%20amount.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHELOC%20lenders%20typically%20allow%20combined%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Floan-to-value-ratio-mortgage-refinancing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloan-to-value%20ratios%3C%2Fa%3E%20up%20to%2080%25%20or%2090%25.%20Your%20CLTV%20is%20the%20ratio%20that%20shows%20the%20balance%20of%20any%20loans%20you%20have%20on%20the%20property%20compared%20to%20the%20value%20of%20your%20home.%20If%20your%20home%20is%20worth%20%24500%2C000%20and%20you%20still%20owe%20%24200%2C000%20on%20your%20mortgage%2C%20you%20have%20a%20CLTV%20of%2040%25%20(200%2C000%2F500%2C000%3D0.4).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20out%20the%20maximum%20amount%20you%20could%20borrow%20with%20a%20HELOC%2C%20multiply%20your%20home's%20current%20value%20by%20your%20HELOC%20lender's%20maximum%20CLTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20your%20lender%20has%20a%20max%20CLTV%20of%2080%25%2C%20and%20your%20home%20is%20worth%20%24500%2C000%20with%20%24200%2C000%20remaining%20on%20your%20mortgage%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E500%2C000%20%C3%97%200.8%20%3D%20400%2C000%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20subtract%20your%20remaining%20mortgage%20balance%20from%20this%20number.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E400%2C000%20-%20200%2C000%20%3D%20200%2C000%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20example%2C%20you%20could%20get%20a%20HELOC%20with%20a%20line%20of%20credit%20up%20to%20%24200%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20homeowners%20may%20have%20access%20to%20even%20more%20cash%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20much%20of%20their%20first%20mortgage%20they%20have%20left%20to%20pay%20and%20how%20much%20equity%20they%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Reasons%20to%20get%20a%20HELOC%5C%22%3EReasons%20to%20get%20a%20HELOC%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20could%20HELOCs%20be%20a%20good%20idea%20right%20now%3F%20One%20of%20the%20main%20draws%20of%20these%20loans%20is%20that%20they're%20incredibly%20flexible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20HELOCs%20work%20similarly%20to%20credit%20cards%2C%20homeowners%20don't%20need%20to%20borrow%20the%20full%20amount%20of%20credit%20they're%20given%20by%20a%20lender.%20This%20can%20help%20you%20save%20on%20interest%2C%20since%20you'll%20only%20pay%20interest%20on%20the%20money%20you%20end%20up%20borrowing%2C%20not%20the%20full%20amount%20you're%20approved%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20have%20that%20line%20of%20credit%20available%20to%20draw%20from%20over%20time%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20customers%20repeatedly%20tap%20into%20their%20HELOC%20over%20time%20for%20various%20needs%2C%20home%20improvement%2C%20paying%20for%20large%20medical%20expenses%2C%20travel%2C%20what%20have%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Boyd%20says.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20that%20HELOC%20on%20hand%20gives%20you%20the%20opportunity%20to%20have%20immediate%20access%20to%20credit%20without%20having%20to%20go%20through%20a%20new%20application%20process%20every%20single%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20get%20a%20HELOC%20over%20a%20home%20equity%20loan%3F%20Home%20equity%20loans%20can%20be%20a%20good%20option%20if%20you%20know%20exactly%20how%20much%20you%20need%20to%20borrow%20and%20you%20want%20the%20stability%20of%20a%20fixed%20rate%20and%20fixed%20monthly%20payment.%20HELOCs%20come%20with%20variable%20rates%2C%20which%20make%20them%20less%20predictable.%20But%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20drop%20this%20year%2C%20which%20means%20getting%20a%20HELOC%20might%20be%20the%20smarter%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20rates%20start%20to%20come%20back%20down%20again%2C%20borrowers%20in%20a%20HELOC%20will%20automatically%20benefit%20from%20those%20lower%20rates%2C%20whereas%20borrowers%20who%20have%20financed%20into%20a%20fixed%20rate%20option%20would%20have%20to%20refinance%20out%20of%20that%20in%20order%20to%20benefit%20from%20lower%20interest%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20Boyd%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Shopping%20for%20a%20HELOC%20lender%5C%22%3EShopping%20for%20a%20HELOC%20lender%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERates%20are%20often%20a%20big%20factor%20when%20shopping%20for%20a%20lender%2C%20and%20rightfully%20so%2C%20but%20they%20shouldn't%20be%20the%20only%20thing%20you're%20thinking%20about%20as%20you%20look%20for%20the%20right%20HELOC%20lender%20for%20you.%20Be%20sure%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20overall%20cost%20of%20the%20HELOC%20as%20well%2C%20including%20closing%20costs%20and%20annual%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20also%20consider%20a%20lender's%20reputation%20and%20any%20additional%20features%20or%20benefits%20it%20can%20offer.%20For%20example%2C%20Boyd%20says%20