an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkrishi.icar.gov.in%2Fjspui%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F69423%2F2%2FAvacado%2520chapter.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edocument%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20avocado%20is%20a%20tropical%20to%20subtropical%20fruit%20that%20struggles%20with%20the%20hot%20and%20frosty%20winds%20of%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20imported%2010%20saplings%20from%20Israel%2C%20and%20now%20I%20have%20a%2010-acre%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F238554%2Fhow-to-grow-avocado-plant-pot-balcony-home-amritsar-farmer-india-gop94%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20avocado%20plantation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Bhopal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20this%20urban%20farmer%20manage%20to%20successfully%20grow%20avocados%20in%20Bhopal%3F%20He%20provides%20an%20insight%20into%20his%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Farming%20was%20never%20my%20plan%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Harshit%20says%20that%20farming%20was%20not%20even%20%E2%80%9Cremotely%20on%20his%20plans%20for%20the%20future%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20he%20was%20interested%20in%20marketing%20and%20after%20his%20schooling%2C%20he%20went%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20study%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20from%20my%20family%20is%20in%20farming%20and%20neither%20did%20I%20ever%20think%20that%20I%20would%20end%20up%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector.%20In%202017%2C%20I%20was%20pursuing%20a%20BBA%20degree%20and%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20career%20in%20marketing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20was%20very%20interested%20in%20health%20and%20fitness%20and%20that%20is%20what%20led%20him%20to%20pursue%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAvocados%20were%20very%20easily%20available%20to%20us%20and%20high%20in%20nutrition.%20I%20used%20to%20love%20eating%20them%20and%20consumed%20them%20almost%20every%20day%20in%20the%20UK.%20One%20day%2C%20I%20just%20flipped%20the%20box%20and%20saw%20the%20packing%20which%20said%20it%20was%20made%20in%20Israel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaken%20aback%2C%20he%20started%20researching%20more%20on%20how%20a%20dry%20and%20hot%20country%20like%20Israel%20can%20grow%20avocados.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20started%20with%20a%20few%20plants%20and%20now%20has%20a%2010%20acre%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350002%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsh%20started%20with%20a%20few%20plants%20and%20now%20has%20a%2010-acre%20farm.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20soil%20and%20temperature%20it%20needed%20to%20grow.%20It%20needs%20a%20temperature%20below%2030%20degrees%20and%20acidic%20soil%20with%20good%20drainage.%20I%20was%20very%20intrigued%20and%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20how%20Israel%20did%20it%20with%20such%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F139546%2Ftemperatures-water-atms-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20temperatures%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUpon%20research%2C%20I%20found%20out%20that%20Israel%20has%20successfully%20grown%20various%20varieties%20under%20controlled%20conditions%20and%20has%20even%20made%20new%20hybrid%20varieties.%20The%20country%20has%20been%20exporting%20the%20fruit%20for%20decades%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20market%20enthusiast%2C%20Harhsit%20realised%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20eating%20the%20fruit%20would%20soon%20catch%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20huge%20demand%20for%20the%20fruit%20in%20the%20west%20which%20means%20that%20it%20will%20reach%20India%20soon.%20This%20gave%20me%20an%20idea%20and%20an%20opportunity%20to%20capitalise%20on%20it.%20I%20thought%20that%20if%20I%20can%20enter%20the%20market%20early%20on%2C%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20greater%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20was%20enthusiastic%20about%20learning%20farming%20from%20the%20farmers%20in%20Israel%20and%20decided%20to%20try%20it%20out%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20cut%20short%20an%20internship%20I%20was%20doing%20at%20the%20time%20and%20go%20to%20Israel.%20I%20found%20a%20farmer%20who%20was%20gracious%20enough%20to%20help%20me%20learn%20the%20entire%20process.%20I%20stayed%20with%20him%2C%20and%20he%20taught%20me%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20avocado%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20grow%20healthy%20avocadoes%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20his%20routine%20in%20Israel%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20daily%20routine%20there%20started%20with%20waking%20up%20at%205%20am.%20We%20would%20work%20in%20the%20fields%20only%20during%20the%20morning%20hours%20until%2010.%20Then%2C%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20he%20would%20introduce%20me%20to%20various%20industry%20experts%2C%20such%20as%20the%20greenhouse%20managers%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340703%2Fkota-student-aryan-singh-invented-ai-powered-agrobot-runs-on-solar-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eirrigation%20specialists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20exporters%2C%20and%20marketers.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20training%20period%2C%20he%20invited%20them%20to%20India.%20%E2%80%9CI%20brought%20my%20farmer%20friends%20over%20in%202018.%20My%20mentor%20and%20the%20nursery%20owner%20conducted%20soil%20tests%20and%20assessed%20the%20climate%20conditions%20in%20Bhopal.%20They%20also%20visited%20other%20farms%20growing%20citrus%20and%20mango.%20After%20evaluating%20the%20area%2C%20they%20suggested%20that%20a%20garden%20could%20thrive%20in%20Bhopal.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20identified%20specific%20avocado%20varieties%20that%20would%20be%20suitable%20for%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20while%20India%20lacks%20high-quality%20avocados%20and%20specific%20varieties%2C%20Israel%20has%20excellent%20rootstocks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20import%20these%20rootstocks%20from%20Israel%20and%20began%20planning%20his%20first%20consignment%2C%20which%20took%20place%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20import%20process%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20lengthy%2C%20complicated%2C%20and%20full%20of%20regulations%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20adhere%20to.%20In%202019%2C%20I%20struggled%20with%20the%20import%20procedure%2C%20causing%20my%20consignment%20to%20be%20delayed%20until%202020%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20went%20to%20Israel%20to%20learn%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20avocado%20farming.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350093%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsh%20went%20to%20Israel%20to%20learn%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20avocado%20farming.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThen%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20struck%2C%20and%20both%20India%20and%20Israel%20went%20into%20lockdown.%20This%20resulted%20in%20yet%20another%20delay%20of%20one%20year%20for%20my%20consignment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinally%2C%20in%202021%2C%20I%20received%20my%20first%20shipment%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289888%2Fharshit-godha-bhopal-grows-avocado-nursery-farming-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavocado%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Israel%2C%20which%20I%20planted%20in%20my%20own%20orchards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20was%20able%20to%20grow%20this%20batch%20of%20avocados%20in%20a%20polyhouse%20nursery%20the%20same%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20have%20not%20made%20the%20fruit%20commercial%20yet%2C%20the%20yield%20was%20shared%20among%20my%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20I%20planted%20the%20avocado%20plants%2C%20they%20were%20kept%20in%20the%20nursery%20until%202023.%20Finally%2C%20in%20March%202023%2C%20I%20planted%20them%20in%20the%20fields.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20first%20year%20the%20crop%20will%20be%20commercially%20viable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20now%20sells%20avocado%20plants%20all%20over%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20says%20that%20he%20uses%20Israeli%20technology%20to%20irrigate%20his%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20employ%20advanced%20techniques%20that%20allow%20us%20to%20control%20water%20distribution%20precisely%20to%20the%20root%20zone%20of%20each%20plant.%20Instead%20of%20using%20flood%20irrigation%2C%20which%20wastes%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20water%2C%20we%20ensure%20that%20each%20plant%20receives%20the%20exact%20amount%20of%20water%20and%20fertiliser%20it%20needs%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20topography%20of%20the%20orchard%2C%20you%20will%20have%20an%20even%20distribution%20of%20water%20for%20each%20and%20every%20plan%2C%20he%20stresses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETips%20for%20new%20urban%20farmers%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20planting%20avocados%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20keep%20a%20few%20things%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20says%20that%20you%20need%20a%20reliable%20water%20source%20or%20should%20practise%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20especially%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%20hot%20climatic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20regions%20like%20the%20Northeast%2C%20natural%20rainwater%20is%20usually%20sufficient.%20For%20other%20areas%20like%20Punjab%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20or%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20a%20dependable%20water%20source%20is%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20consideration%20is%20choosing%20the%20right%20variety%20of%20avocado%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CI%20offer%20a%20100%25%20buy-back%20guarantee%2C%20ensuring%20that%20my%20customers%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20problems%20selling%20their%20produce.%20I%20source%20the%20plants%20from%20Israel%2C%20where%20extensive%20research%20has%20been%20conducted%20on%20avocados%20over%20the%20last%2060%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-3-1715758593.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20says%20that%20you%20need%20a%20reliable%20water%20source%20or%20should%20practise%20rainwater%20harvesting%20to%20grow%20avocados.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-3-1715758593.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-3-1715758593-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-3-1715758593-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-3-1715758593-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-3-1715758593-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350004%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsh%20says%20that%20you%20need%20a%20reliable%20water%20source%20or%20should%20practise%20rainwater%20harvesting%20to%20grow%20avocados.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20developed%20varieties%20resistant%20to%20drought%20and%20poor%20water%20quality%20that%20yield%20high%20productivity%20even%20in%20extreme%20climates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20plants%20sold%20in%20South%20India%20for%20Rs%20500%20each%20may%20be%20grown%20from%20random%20avocado%20seeds%20and%20then%20grafted%2C%20leading%20to%20variability%20in%20quality.%20My%20plants%2C%20which%20cost%20Rs%202%2C500%20each%2C%20are%20grown%20on%20commercial%20rootstocks%20of%20specific%20avocados%20developed%20in%20Israel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvocado%20plants%20consist%20of%20two%20parts%3A%20the%20rootstock%20(the%20part%20below%20the%20graft)%20and%20the%20cultivar.%20The%20rootstock%20imparts%20certain%20properties%20to%20the%20entire%20plant%2C%20such%20as%20high%20yield%20and%20manageable%20canopy%20size.%20This%20allows%20for%20easier%20harvesting%20at%20heights%20of%20just%2010%20to%2012%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoosing%20the%20right%20rootstock%20and%20variety%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seeking%20the%20appropriate%20support%2C%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRemember%2C%20different%20climates%20require%20different%20management%20practices%20and%20techniques.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20methods%20used%20in%20South%20India%20differ%20from%20those%20used%20in%20Central%20India%20where%20I%20am%20based.%20Expecting%20similar%20results%20from%20cheaper%20plants%20without%20considering%20these%20factors%20may%20lead%20to%20disappointment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20Pictures%20Credit%3A%20Harshit%20Godha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715777750000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Urban%20farmer%20Harshit%20Godha%20took%20inspiration%20from%20Israeli%20farmers%20growing%20avocadoes%20and%20has%20successfully%20grown%20the%20fruit%20in%20India.%20He%20shares%20how%20you%20can%20grow%20them%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engag