href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F163949%2Fjakkur-bengaluru-lake-pollution-cleaning-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especies%20of%20flora%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20you%20think%20reside%20within%20this%2025-acre%20land%3F%20Take%20a%20guess.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20850%20species%20and%20counting%2C%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20Chaturvedi.%20In%20this%20forest-like%20ecosystem%20that%20he%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20few%20years%20cultivating%2C%20bamboo%20and%20cactus%20befriend%20each%20other%2C%20while%20crickets%2C%20butterflies%20and%20insects%20stop%20by%20to%20pay%20their%20respects%20to%20the%20honeysuckle.%20The%20air%20is%20crisp%20and%20the%20walk%20is%20therapeutic%20for%20Chaturvedi%2C%20who%20pauses%20to%20put%20his%20experience%20into%20words%3B%20then%20proceeds%20to%20say%20that%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20justice.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20most%20taken%20aback%20by%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20optimistic%20view%20are%20the%20naysayers%20who%20were%20convinced%20that%20this%20particular%20posting%20in%20the%20highlands%20of%20Uttarakhand%20would%20be%20a%20test%20of%20the%20IFS%20officer%E2%80%99s%20patience.%20Their%20discouragement%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20most%20of%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20predecessors%20had%20detested%20being%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20god-forsaken%20area%2C%20made%20the%20officer%20sceptical.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302635%2Fladakh-ministry-of-education-score-new-heights-role-of-dedicated-teachers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20harsh%20terrain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20remoteness%20of%20the%20place%2C%20did%20nothing%20to%20ease%20his%20woes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20nine%20years%20since%20he%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20conservator%20of%20forest%20research%20(Chaturvedi%20was%20promoted%20to%20head%20of%20the%20wing%20in%202020)%2C%20this%20terrain%20evolved%20into%20a%20blessing.%20As%20Chaturvedi%20and%20his%20team%20discovered%2C%20not%20only%20was%20it%20a%20favourable%20home%20for%20Nainital%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98miracle%20plant%E2%80%99%20Patwa%2C%20but%20also%20a%20host%20of%20other%20plant%20species%20that%20are%20in%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature)%20red%20list%20and%20classified%20as%20%E2%80%98threatened%E2%80%99%20by%20Uttarakhand%20board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20has%20been%20working%20closely%20to%20conserve%20plant%20habitats%20and%20protect%20them%20from%20illegal%20trade.%20They%20are%20also%20innovating%20ways%20to%20grow%20them%20in%20their%20natural%20habitats%20and%20in%20their%20research%20centres%20as%20well.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20scale%20these%20plant%20populations%20at%20their%20original%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IFS%20Officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%20has%20dedicated%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20to%20conserving%20endemic%20plant%20species%20in%20Nainital%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349420%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIFS%20Officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%20has%20dedicated%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20to%20conserving%20endemic%20plant%20species%20in%20Nainital%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chaturvedi%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20today%2C%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20work%20in%20this%20domain%20is%20being%20applauded%2C%20in%202015%2C%20his%20path%20looked%20very%20different.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehighlighted%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dsanjeev%2Bchaturvedi%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26rlz%3D1C1YTUH_enIN1048IN1048%26oq%3Dsanjeev%2Bchaturvedi%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUqBggAEEUYOzIGCAAQRRg7MgcIARAhGKABMgcIAhAhGKAB0gEINTk0NGowajSoAgCwAgA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20officer%E2%80%99s%20scope%20of%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20field%20of%20anti-corruption.%20Impressive%20and%20courageous%20though%20the%20operations%20were%2C%20they%20resulted%20in%20chargesheets%2C%20suspension%20orders%2C%20low%20gradings%20in%20Annual%20Performance%20Reports%20(APAR)%2C%20dismissals%20and%20frequent%20transfers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20objective%20was%20always%20the%20same%3A%20to%20halt%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20crackdown%20on%20corruption.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20a%20firm%20belief%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20true%20democracy%20to%20prevail%2C%20adhering%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20was%20the%20way%20forward%E2%80%9D%2C%20Chaturvedi%20never%20backed%20down.%20And%20in%202015%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20for%20emergent%20leadership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20leader%20then%20and%20now%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20native%20has%20prided%20himself%20on%20displaying%20integrity%20even%20in%20the%20most%20sticky%20spots.%20Early%20on%2C%20he%20resolved%20never%20to%20see%20transfers%20as%20a%20punishment.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20transfer%20is%20part%20of%20your%20career%20and%20as%20a%20servant%20of%20your%20nation%2C%20it%20is%20your%20duty%20to%20do%20it%20with%20utmost%20commitment%20and%20professionalism%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said%20five%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20not%20only%20has%20he%20stayed%20true%20to%20those%20words%2C%20but%20has%20found%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348647%2Fcancer-shelter-in-india-access-life-ankeet-dave-girish-nair-children-paediatric-care-in-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurpose%20in%20his%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20here%20in%20the%20Haldwani%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBlazing%20a%20trail%20in%20conservation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20head%20of%20the%20research%20wing%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20which%20focuses%20on%20the%20conservation%20of%20threatened%20plant%20species%2C%20the%2050-year-old%20officer%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20biodiversity%20protection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20crucial%20in%20this%20area.%20Uttarakhand%20has%20over%2043%20types%20of%20different%20forests%20and%20three%20major%20agro-climate%20zones%3A%20tropical%2C%20temperate%20and%20alpine.%20The%20altitude%20of%20the%20place%20ranges%20from%20300%20m%20up%20to%20the%206%2C800%20m%20high%20Nanda%20Devi%20Peak.%20As%20you%20can%20see%2C%20the%20flora%20here%20experiences%20a%20very%20diverse%20climate.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1-1715256743.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Naagchatri%20plant%20is%20endemic%20to%20Uttarakhand%20and%20its%20roots%20contain%20